SUMMARY:From AI to ROI: Turning Pilots Into Scalable Impact
DESCRIPTION:Data Science Raleigh\nEvery enterprise has its share of AI pro
 of-of-concepts—many promising\, few enduring. This webinar goes beyond t
 he hype to explore what it actually takes to move from experimental AI pil
 ots to sustained\, enterprise-wide value. We’ll dig into the operational
 \, organizational\, and architectural levers that help AI investments move
  out of the sandbox and into the business mainstream.\n\nThrough expert di
 scussion and real-world examples\, we’ll explore the friction points tha
 t stall scaling efforts—and what forward-thinking leaders are doing to o
 vercome them. If you're leading or influencing AI adoption in your organiz
 ation\, this session is about turning progress into performance.\n\n**Key 
 Takeaways:**\n\n1️⃣ **Real Product Experience:** See full workflows in
  motion—not just the highlights.\n\n2️⃣ **Operational Readiness:** W
 hat’s required in terms of data infrastructure\, governance\, and cross-
 functional collaboration to support scaled AI.\n\n3️⃣ **Organizational
  Design:** How roles\, incentives\, and workflows evolve when AI becomes a
  core operating capability.\n\n4️⃣ **Sustaining Value:** Strategies fo
 r continuous iteration\, observability\, and measuring long-term ROI from 
 AI investments.\n\n**[Register here](https://hubs.ly/Q041vh4c0)**
