SUMMARY:Agentic AI in Action: 10-Minute Demo Spotlights from the Frontier 
 Q2
DESCRIPTION:Data Science Raleigh\nExplore the real-world impact of Agentic
  AI in our fast-paced\, insight-packed virtual showcase. Each 10-minute se
 ssion features a live demo from a leading innovator in the Agentic AI spac
 e—highlighting practical applications\, dynamic workflows\, and tangible
  business outcomes.\n\nThis isn't just another pitch session. It’s a cur
 ated look at how agent-based systems are driving intelligent automation\, 
 adaptive planning\, and cross-functional orchestration across industries. 
 You’ll meet the minds behind these technologies and see firsthand how th
 ey’re redefining what's possible in enterprise AI.\n\n**What You'll Lear
 n:**\n\n1️⃣ **Autonomous Workflows:** See how agentic systems plan\, c
 oordinate\, and execute complex tasks across tools and teams.\n\n2️⃣ *
 *Dynamic Decisioning:** Explore examples of contextual reasoning\, goal al
 ignment\, and memory-enhanced agents in action.\n\n3️⃣**Practical Inte
 gration:** Understand what it takes to embed agentic AI into your stack—
 without overhauling everything.\n\nEngage live with founders and builders 
 shaping the future of autonomous enterprise solutions.\n\nYou’re short o
 n time but deep on curiosity. This format respects both—cutting straight
  to the tech and the teams behind it. No filler\, no fluff. Just signal.\n
 \n**[Register here](https://hubs.ly/Q042cVj20)**
